fact WorkItem(
  id: "WI-154",
  description: "scaland resync — rule attribute flags [simp] / [unfold] / [hint] + bare-flag desugar form. Mirror WI-139/140/141 from rustland into scaland. Bare `[simp]` desugars to `[simp: true]` (WI-140). Equational rules cite-required by default unless `[simp]` flag (WI-139). [hint] auto-included from any proof in the enclosing scope chain (WI-141). Loader-side: store flags in the rule's MetaBlock for later use by prove/check (WI-157 — does not exist yet on Scala side, but the metadata needs to be preserved through parse and load so WI-157 can pick it up later). Files: scaland/core/src/main/scala/anthill/parse/AnthillParser.scala (meta_entry parser — accept bare-flag form), parse/IR.scala (verify MetaEntry handling), load/Loader.scala (preserve meta on rules). Acceptance: sbt test green; new ParseTest cases for [simp] bare-flag form parsing identically to [simp: true].",
  acceptance: [ToolPasses("scaland-sbt-test")],
